      { name: "Diphenhydramine", type: "First-Generation Antihistamine", action: "Blocks H1 histamine receptors, reducing pruritus and providing sedation", sideEffects: "Drowsiness, dry mouth, urinary retention, constipation", contra: "Narrow-angle glaucoma, urinary retention, concurrent MAOI use", pearl: "Sedating effect helps with nighttime pruritus. Caution in older adults due to anticholinergic effects." }
